  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink1-kilavi"> puṟattoḻukkattilē neṭunāḷoḻuki, ‘itu takātu’ eṉat teḷinta maṉattaṉāy
          mīṇṭu talaiviyōṭukūṭi oḻuṅkāniṉṟa talaimakaṉ tōḻiyōṭu collāṭi, ‘yāṉ avvāṟoḻuka nīyir
          niṉaitta tiṟam yātu?’ eṉṟāṟku avaḷ colliyatu. </p>
        <p xml:lang="en">  <hi rend="italic"> [translation to be added ]</hi> </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Aink1">
          <l>vāḻi yātaṉ vāḻi yaviṉi</l>
          <l> neṟpala polika poṉperitu ciṟakka</l>
          <l> veṉavēṭ ṭōḷē yāyē yāmē</l>
          <l> naṉaiya kāñcic ciṉaiya ciṟumīṉ</l>
          <l> yāṇa rūraṉ vāḻka </l>
          <l> pāṇaṉum vāḻka veṉavēṭ ṭēmē. </l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">

          <l> 'Long live Ātaṉ! Long live Aviṉi!</l>
          <l> May [our] many rice plants multiply!</l>
          <l> May [we] amass much gold!' </l>
          <l> — that's what our mother wants.</l>
          <l> As for us:</l>
          <l> 'The man from the fertile village </l>
          <l> of budding Portia trees </l>
          <l> and little egg-bearing fish: </l>
          <l> May he live long, and may the bard live long!' </l>
          <l>— that's what we have been wanting. </l>

          <lg type="alternate">
            <l> 'Long live Ātaṉ! Long live Aviṉi!</l>
          <l> May [our] many rice plants multiply!</l>
          <l> May [we] amass much gold!' </l>
          <l> — that's what our mother wants.</l>
          <l> As for us:</l>
          <l> 'The man from the fertile village </l>
          <l> of budding Portia trees </l>
          <l> and little egg-bearing fish: </l>
          <l> May he live long, and may the bard live long!' </l>
          <l>— that's what we have been wanting. </l>
          <trailer>translation by Thomas Lehmann</trailer>
          </lg>
        </lg>
      </div>
